---
---
<section style="border-top: 1px solid #21262d;">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-10 font-mono" style="color: #e6edf3;">
      <span style="color: #b5843a;">#</span> How it works
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">

      <div class="relative">
        <div class="text-xs font-mono font-bold mb-3 tabular-nums" style="color: #b5843a;">01</div>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #8b949e;">
          Your app sends errors to
          <span class="font-mono text-xs px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded" style="background-color: #161b22; color: #c9d1d9; border: 1px solid #21262d;">POST /api/v1/events</span>
          — accepted immediately, processed async.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="text-xs font-mono font-bold mb-3 tabular-nums" style="color: #b5843a;">02</div>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #8b949e;">
          BugBarn fingerprints, groups, and stores everything in SQLite on your server.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="text-xs font-mono font-bold mb-3 tabular-nums" style="color: #b5843a;">03</div>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #8b949e;">
          Browse issues, set alerts, and get weekly digests — fully in your own infrastructure.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="text-xs font-mono font-bold mb-3 tabular-nums" style="color: #b5843a;">04</div>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #8b949e;">
          Privacy scrubbing runs automatically — emails, IPs, UUIDs, and secrets are redacted before storage.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
